## ðŸ”¹ 231. Power of Two

**Language:** C++

```cpp
class Solution {
public:
    bool isPowerOfTwo(int n) {
        return n > 0 && not (n & n - 1);
    }
};

ðŸ”¹ 326. Power of Three
Language: C++
class Solution {
public:
    bool isPowerOfThree(int n) {
        if (n <= 0) return false;
        while (n % 3 == 0) {
            n /= 3;
        }
        return n == 1;
    }
};
ðŸ”¹ 415. Add Strings
Language: Python
class Solution(object):
    def addStrings(self, num1, num2):
        num1 = int(num1)
        num2 = int(num2)
        return str(num1 + num2)

